item.dc:creator: @Weibs Weibs
item.description:
@Weibs wrote:

SRL.scar isn’t meant for you to run it. It just has some consts, vars, and a few procedures, and then it includes all of the other main includes, like all of the core files.

You use SRL.scar by including it, like this:

[scar]Program New;
{.include SRl/SRL.scar}[/scar]
